### Course API Test Requests

### Get all courses with pagination
GET {{host}}/api/courses?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&searchTerm=

### Get all courses without pagination
GET {{host}}/api/courses/all

### Get course by ID
GET {{host}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}

### Create a new course
POST {{host}}/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Introduction to .NET Core",
  "description": "Learn the fundamentals of .NET Core development, including dependency injection, middleware, and API development.",
  "level": 0,
  "courseType": 0,
  "price": 99.99,
  "thumbnailUrl": "https://example.com/thumbnails/dotnet-course.jpg"
}

### Update an existing course
PUT {{host}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Advanced .NET Core Development",
  "description": "Master advanced .NET Core concepts including Clean Architecture, CQRS, and Domain-Driven Design.",
  "level": 2,
  "price": 149.99
}

### Delete a course
DELETE {{host}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}

### Get courses by instructor
GET {{host}}/api/courses/instructor/{{instructorId}}

### Get courses by status
GET {{host}}/api/courses/status/Published

### Get courses by level (0=Beginner, 1=Intermediate, 2=Advanced)
GET {{host}}/api/courses/level/0

### Get courses by type
GET {{host}}/api/courses/type/0

### Update course status
PATCH {{host}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

"Published"

### Variables
@host = https://localhost:5001
@courseId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@instructorId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 